title: How to Do a Man Bun | AXE | Instagroom
description:
This is how Teo ties his hair before playing football. Vamos! 

THE TOOLS:
AXE Natural Look Softening Cream 
Hairband

THE STEPS:
1. Mix cream between fingers
2. Rake into bun
3. Lock it with a hairband

transcripts: I only tie my hair when I’m about to play football. During the game I don’t want to have hair in my eyes. I scoop a finger of cream, mix it between my fingers, and I rake my hair back into a loose bun, and then I lock it with a band. (Makes a sound). That’s it. Vamos!
